skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: freedom festival
des:
The Freedom Festival is for attendees of the Freedom Festival in Provo, Utah. Using the skill, festival goers can find out what events are going on when. You can use this skill by saying “Alexa, ask Freedom Festival what is going on today” to get that day’s event schedule. 

There are some joke answers as well, so be sure to look out for our messaging, or talk to a friend to find out what to ask.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
